{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2cd59910f8","title":"祝贺中苏友好条约签订两周年致斯大林电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a61cc93d06","index":0,"year":1952,"month":2,"day":11,"articleId":"2cd59910f8"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9aa20335f3","type":"title","text":"祝贺中苏友好条约签订两周年致斯大林电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"2cd59910f8"},{"id":"cda988888a","type":"paragraph","text":"苏维埃社会主义共和国联盟部长会议主席斯大林同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"2cd59910f8"},{"id":"4dc2a77c6b","type":"paragraph","text":"值此中苏友好同盟互助条约签订二周年之际，我代表中华人民共和国政府和人民谨向伟大的苏联人民、苏联政府和您表示深切的感谢与热烈的祝贺。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"2cd59910f8"},{"id":"e1ab37e545","type":"paragraph","text":"我们感谢两年来苏联政府和人民依照中苏友好同盟互助条约及其有关各协定的精神，给予中国政府和人民热诚的、概的援助，这些援助大大帮助了新中国经济的恢复和发展及国家的巩固","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"2cd59910f8"},{"id":"03c9e16570","type":"paragraph","text":"我们祝贺中苏两国人民伟大友请的日臻亲密。中苏两国强大的同盟是不可战胜的力量，是反对帝国主义侵略和维护远东和平及安全的坚强保证，也是争取世界和平的伟大事业胜利的保证。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"2cd59910f8"},{"id":"25f32c4511","type":"paragraph","text":"中苏两国人民牢不可破的友好团结方罗！","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"2cd59910f8"},{"id":"54e5ce1b78","type":"paragraph","text":"中华人民共和国中央人民政府主席毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"2cd59910f8"},{"id":"28a82e5f8d","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五二年二月十一日北京","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"2cd59910f8"}],"page":{"id":"607e36f0f2","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"2cd59910f8","start":380,"end":380}}}},"__N_SSG":true}